name: 贾森·赖利
introduction: Jason's film credits include the short films "Sugar Coated" and "I Shall," as well as roles in feature films "Zombie Night" and "Space Zombies". He's performed sketch and improv comedy as part of The Second City Touring Company. Jason's theatre credits include performances in "Unidentified Human Remains and the True Nature of Love", written by acclaimed Canadian playwright Brad Fraser and "Agatha Christie's: The Mousetrap" during its uninterrupted 27-year run in Toronto. Jason has also performed in several original works at the Toronto Fringe Festival.
